{"ID":270121, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"121\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs120.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs122.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 121<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">palmed upon the people by the priests, and this is the only reason why we ever thought of answering\n  them.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Fifteenth&mdash;&ldquo;Do the Mormons baptize in the name of &lsquo;Joe&rsquo; Smith?&rdquo;<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">No, but if they did, it would be as valid as the baptism administered by the sectarian priests.<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Sixteenth&mdash;&ldquo;If the Mormon doctrine is true, what has become of all those who died since the\n  days of the Apostles?&rdquo;<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">All those who have not had an opportunity of hearing the Gospel,<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> and being administered unto\n  by an inspired man<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> in the flesh, must have it hereafter, before they can be finally judged.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Seventeenth&mdash;&ldquo;Does not &lsquo;Joe&rsquo; Smith profess to be Jesus Christ?&rdquo;<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">No, but he professes to be His brother, as all other Saints have done and now do: Matt. 12:49,\n  50, &ldquo;And He stretched forth His hand toward His disciples and said, Behold my mother and my\n  brethren; for whosoever shall do the will of my Father, which is in heaven, the same is my brother,\n  and sister, and mother.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Eighteenth&mdash;&ldquo;Is there anything in the Bible which licenses you to believe in revelation\n  now-a-days?&rdquo;<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Is there anything that does not authorize us to believe so? If there is, we have, as yet, not been\n  able to find it.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Nineteenth&mdash;&ldquo;Is not the canon of the Scriptures full?&rdquo;<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">If it is, there is a great defect in the book, or else it would have said so.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Twentieth&mdash;&ldquo;What are the fundamental principles of your religion?&rdquo;<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The fundamental principles of our religion are the testimony of the Apostles and Prophets,\n  concerning Jesus Christ, that He died, was buried, and rose again the third day,<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> and ascended into\n  heaven;<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> and all other things which pertain to our religion are only appendages to it. But in\n  connection with these, we believe in the gift of the Holy Ghost,<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> the power of faith,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> the enjoyment\n  of the spiritual gifts<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> according to the will of God,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> the restoration of the house of Israel,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> and the\n  final triumph of truth.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I published the foregoing answers to save myself the trouble of repeating the same a thousand\n  times over and over again. (May 8, 1838.) DHC 3:28-30.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113415\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113415)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113415)\">D&amp;C 22:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116618\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116618)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116618)\">D&amp;C 137:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115401\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115401)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115401)\">D&amp;C 107:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107992\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107992)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107992)\">Matt. 12:49-50<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109578\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109578)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109578)\">1 Cor. 15:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113352\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113352)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113352)\">D&amp;C 20:23-24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108886\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108886)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108886)\">John 20:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108905\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108905)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108905)\">Acts 1:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111627\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111627)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111627)\">Mosiah 15:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112598\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112598)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112598)\">3 Ne. 11:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112650\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112650)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112650)\">3 Ne. 18:39<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112693\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112693)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112693)\">3 Ne. 26:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113353\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113353)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113353)\">D&amp;C 20:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108949\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108949)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108949)\">Acts 2:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112967\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112967)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112967)\">Moro. 7:33<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113016\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113016)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113016)\">Moro. 10:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109506\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109506)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109506)\">1 Cor. 12:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109309\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109309)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109309)\">Rom. 8:27<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109710\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109710)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109710)\">Gal. 1:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110467\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110467)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110467)\">1 Pet. 4:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111105\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111105)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111105)\">2 Ne. 2:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112546\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112546)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112546)\">3 Ne. 5:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113928\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113928)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113928)\">D&amp;C 46:30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114157\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114157)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114157)\">D&amp;C 63:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111007\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111007)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111007)\">1 Ne. 15:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111123\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111123)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111123)\">2 Ne. 3:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}